hosp_report: Hungarian gov started reporting deaths from a separate page compiling deaths: https://koronavirus.gov.hu/elhunytak
No archive page for death, numbers pulled from CSSE data
Started reporting home quarantine and not hospital quarantine; No archive page for death, numbers pulled from CSSE data
Started reporting in hospital and ventilator numbers (https://koronavirus.gov.hu/cikkek/1763-fore-nott-beazonositott-fertozottek-szama-es-elhunyt-14-idos-kronikus-beteg)
